test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 0 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a5c4ef99ec0>([57])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a5c4ef99ec0> = [[57], [57], [57]].count
 +  and   0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a5c4ef99ec0>([1, 57])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a5c4ef99ec0> = [[57], [57], [57]].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 19 == 57
 +  where 19 = <built-in function prod>([19])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
